Casey, 1914: 358 [primary homonym of 
<taxonomicName class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Cicindela" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="239" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mirabilis">
