</taxonomicName>
Laporte, 1835]. Type locality: &quot;Dutch Flat, Placer Co[unty], California&quot; (original citation). Holotype [by monotypy] (♀) in USNM [# 45936].
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="239" pageNumber="240">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Leffler" authorityYear="1980" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Cicindela" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="239" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="purpurea" subSpecies="hatchi">Cicindela purpurea hatchi</taxonomicName>
