<emphasis bold="true" pageId="239" pageNumber="240">CAN</emphasis>
: BC (VCI) 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="239" pageNumber="240">USA</emphasis>
: CA, OR, WA
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="239" pageNumber="240" type="note">
<paragraph pageId="239" pageNumber="240">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="239" pageNumber="240">
This subspecies intergrades with the 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="239" pageNumber="240">lauta</emphasis>
form in the Willamette Valley of Oregon south to Shasta and Modoc Counties in northwestern California (Pearson et al. 2006: 87).
</paragraph>
